        {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "Music is not a human invention. We, humans, strive for uniqueness as individuals and as a species. We are, indeed, special and unique in many cases but we did not invent music."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "There is a plethora of animals that use music and, most of them, use it with the same function: <u>a mating call</u>. We just \"civilized\" it like we do with everything else."
